ğŸ“ Executive Summary

Today I focused on what comes after gaining SSH access: identifying potential paths to escalate privileges.
I used LinPEAS, a well-known Linux privilege escalation enumerator, to map weaknesses across the target system.

This phase is not exploitation, but reconnaissance â€” understanding the security posture from an attackerâ€™s perspective.

